#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:2
msgid "物件组进阶使用"
msgstr "Advanced Usage of Groups"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:4
msgid "前文回顾：:doc:`item_group`"
msgstr "Previous Review: :doc:`item_group`"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:7
msgid "具名物件组"
msgstr "Named Item Groups"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:9
msgid ""
"除了使用 ``Group(...)`` 直接传入多个物件，还可以使用 :class:`~.NamedGroup` 类来创建带有 **具名子物件** 的物件组，例如："
msgstr ""
"In addition to passing multiple items directly to ``Group(...)``, you can also use the :class:`~.NamedGroup` class to "
"create a group with **named child items**, for example:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:11
msgid "group = NamedGroup(title=..., content=...)"
msgstr "group = NamedGroup(title=..., content=...)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:15
msgid ""
"具名物件组的 :meth:`~.NamedGroupMixin.add` 和 :meth:`~.NamedGroupMixin.remove` 等方法也支持使用具名参数来添加/移除具名子物"
"件。"
msgstr ""
"Methods such as :meth:`~.NamedGroupMixin.add` and :meth:`~.NamedGroupMixin.remove` on named item groups also support "
"using keyword arguments to add or remove named child items."

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:17
msgid "访问其具名子物件可以使用类似 ``group['content']`` 的形式，例如："
msgstr "You can access its named child items using syntax like ``group['content']``, for example:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:19
msgid ""
"pair = NamedGroup(src=Circle(), target=Square())\n"
"\n"
"self.play(Transform(pair['src'], pair['target']))"
msgstr ""
"pair = NamedGroup(src=Circle(), target=Square())\n"
"\n"
"self.play(Transform(pair['src'], pair['target']))"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:25
msgid "更多内容请参考 :class:`~.NamedGroupMixin` 与 :class:`~.NamedGroup` 的文档"
msgstr "For more information, see the documentation to :class:`~.NamedGroupMixin` and :class:`~.NamedGroup`."

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:28
msgid "物件的批量复制"
msgstr "Batch Copying of Items"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:30
msgid ""
"举个例子，对于一个圆形物件 ``Circle()``，我们可以在其后面使用 ``* 数量`` 表示 “复制出指定数量的圆形，放到一"
"个 :class:`~.Group` 中”："
msgstr ""
"For example, for a circle item ``Circle()``, we can use ``* number`` after it to mean \"copy the specified number of "
"circles and put them in a :class:`~.Group`\":"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:15
msgid ""
"circles = Circle() * 5\n"
"circles.points.arrange()\n"
"self.show(circles)"
msgstr ""
"circles = Circle() * 5\n"
"circles.points.arrange()\n"
"self.show(circles)circles = Circle() * 5\n"
"circles.points.arrange()\n"
"self.show(circles)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:42
msgid ""
"复制出来的物件都会保持相同的属性和状态，所以他们会重叠在一起， 如果你想让他们排列开来，使用 :meth:`~.Cmpt_Points.arrange` "
"或是 :meth:`~.Cmpt_Points.arrange_in_grid` 会是比较方便的做法。"
msgstr ""
"Copied items will all maintain the same properties and state, so they will overlap. If you want them arranged, "
"using :meth:`~.Cmpt_Points.arrange` or :meth:`~.Cmpt_Points.arrange_in_grid` would be convenient approaches."

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:45
msgid "以下是另一个示例："
msgstr "Here is another example:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:15
msgid ""
"txts = Text('This is some text') * 9\n"
"\n"
"for i, txt in enumerate(txts):\n"
"    txt.points.scale(1 - 0.1 * i)\n"
"    txt.color.fade(0.1 * i)\n"
"\n"
"txts.points.arrange(DOWN, buff=0.05)\n"
"self.show(txts)"
msgstr ""
"txts = Text('This is some text') * 9\n"
"\n"
"for i, txt in enumerate(txts):\n"
"    txt.points.scale(1 - 0.1 * i)\n"
"    txt.color.fade(0.1 * i)\n"
"\n"
"txts.points.arrange(DOWN, buff=0.05)\n"
"self.show(txts)txts = Text('This is some text') * 9\n"
"\n"
"for i, txt in enumerate(txts):\n"
"    txt.points.scale(1 - 0.1 * i)\n"
"    txt.color.fade(0.1 * i)\n"
"\n"
"txts.points.arrange(DOWN, buff=0.05)\n"
"self.show(txts)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:61
msgid "物件组的进阶索引"
msgstr "Advanced Indexing of Item Groups"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:63
msgid "我们已经知道索引的基础用法，可以使用下标索引子物件，或是使用切片得到一组子物件："
msgstr ""
"We already know the basic usage of indexing. We can use subscript to index child items, or use slicing to get a group of "
"child items:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:15
msgid ""
"circles = Circle(radius=0.5) * 10\n"
"circles.points.arrange()\n"
"circles[1].set(color=RED)\n"
"circles[4:7].set(color=BLUE)\n"
"circles.show()\n"
"\n"
"for i, circle in enumerate(circles):\n"
"    txt = Text(str(i), font_size=12).show()\n"
"    txt.points.next_to(circle, DOWN, buff=SMALL_BUFF)"
msgstr ""
"circles = Circle(radius=0.5) * 10\n"
"circles.points.arrange()\n"
"circles[1].set(color=RED)\n"
"circles[4:7].set(color=BLUE)\n"
"circles.show()\n"
"\n"
"for i, circle in enumerate(circles):\n"
"    txt = Text(str(i), font_size=12).show()\n"
"    txt.points.next_to(circle, DOWN, buff=SMALL_BUFF)circles = Circle(radius=0.5) * 10\n"
"circles.points.arrange()\n"
"circles[1].set(color=RED)\n"
"circles[4:7].set(color=BLUE)\n"
"circles.show()\n"
"\n"
"for i, circle in enumerate(circles):\n"
"    txt = Text(str(i), font_size=12).show()\n"
"    txt.points.next_to(circle, DOWN, buff=SMALL_BUFF)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:79
msgid "除了这两种基础方法，你还可以通过以下方式："
msgstr "In addition to these two basic methods, you can also use the following:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/group_advanced_usage.rst:13
msgid ""
"circles = Circle(radius=0.5) * 10\n"
"circles.points.arrange()\n"
"circles.show()\n"
"\n"
"for i, circle in enumerate(circles):\n"
"    txt = Text(str(i)).show()\n"
"    txt.points.next_to(circle, DOWN, buff=SMALL_BUFF)\n"
"\n"
"self.forward()\n"
"self.play(\n"
"    circles[1, 3, 6, 7].anim.set(color=RED, fill_alpha=0.7)\n"
")\n"
"self.forward()\n"
"self.play(\n"
"    circles[True, False, True, True].anim.set(color=BLUE, fill_alpha=0.7)\n"
")\n"
"self.forward()"
